## Configuration (`.env`)

| Variable | Purpose | Default |
|---|---|---|
| `FLASK_ENV` | Flask environment | `development` |
| `APP_ENV` | Application environment | `development` |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Database connection string | `sqlite:///runs.db` |
| `ADMIN_USER_ID` | Super admin user ID | `1` |
| `ALLOW_DB_INIT` | Allow auto-creation of tables | `true` |
| `DEBUG` | Debug mode | `true` |

---

## Deployment

- **Local:** `flask run --debug` or `python app.py` (serves on `0.0.0.0:5000`).
- **Production:** Gunicorn (`gunicorn app:app`), designed to work on **Render** or similar platforms.
- DB tables auto-initialize on startup via [init_db()](file:///c:/Users/Yajat%20Sharma/Programming%20codes/Running-py/app.py#24-137).

